item.title: CVE-2024-3368|2024-05-20T06:00:01.083Z -- Unknown -- All in One SEO
item.description: The All in One SEO WordPress plugin before 4.6.1.1 does not validate and escape some of its Post fields before outputting them back, which could allow users with the contributor role and above to perform Stored Cross-Site Scripting attacks
